Note: Both albums are 320 kbps. And full disclosure, neither of the albums were ripped by me; the debut I got from newalbumreleases.net and the followup from musicbay.co (both are great sites for acquiring newly leaked releases, by the way). I just noticed that 'Sprinter' wasn't available on TPB so I decided to upload it (along with the self-titled debut) in the hopes that others will download it and enjoy it as much as I have
